snippet.title: Ice Age Farmer
snippet.description:
The Ice Age Farmer broadcast looks deeply at the future of our food supply, from the agenda to defile and centralize control to how this must inform our response:  a rapid move back to decentralized, regenerative food system.

I recommend subscribing on another platform such as:

https://iceagefarmer.com/

or https://bitchute.com/iceagefarmer
or https://odysee.com/@iceagefarmer

Follow on telegram:  https://t.me/iceagefarmer
